    "Moreover, these devices generate a huge amount of data (logs) in multiple formats thus overwhelming the log management.",
    "This issue is particularly important for SMEs that usually have limited human resources and managing security can often be a part-time job for a single individual [5].",
    "This makes them an easy target for cybercriminals.",
    "Therefore, a pragmatic approach for SMEs is unified security management.",
    "SIEM system facilitates this with efficient collection of data from disparate log sources into a single system for real-time analysis [6] delivered to a single console."
